oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Osborne Brothers at Antioch College (1957 - 1960?). Announced by Bobby Osborne as the first college engagement the Osborne Brothers have ever played. Osborne Brothers lineup is announced as Bobby and Sonny Osborne, Benny Birchfield-bass; Jimmy Brown-guitar.; Stanley Brothers at Brown County Jamboree, Bean Blossom, Indiana believed to be pre-1964. Other musicians and dates unidentified.
